[b]Introduction[/b]
Rune-X v1 was not a big hit as I expected it to be mainly because of the huge cache and no npc drops since it was Rune-M t p I spent lot of time trying to fix it but I couldn't so I decided to start V2. This will be a PI and will have many of the same features as before but a little more.
[b]Goals[/b] Eco Based Many Bosses A good pking system Atleast 50 players
